<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Guestbook</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Noto Serif SC, Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    #cusdis_thread {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 8px;
      /* box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); */
      background-color: #fff;
    }
    .comments-count {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #555;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      body {
        background-color: #2f2f2f;
        color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #2f2f2f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }
      #cusdis_thread {
        border: 1px solid #555;
        background-color: #2f2f2f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }
      .comments-count {
        color: #ccc;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 10px;
        margin: 20px auto;
      }
      #cusdis_thread {
        padding: 10px;
      }
      .comments-count {
        font-size: 1em;
      }
    }
  </style>
  <script defer src="https://cusdis.com/js/widget/lang/zh-cn.js"></script>
  <script defer src="https://cusdis.com/js/cusdis.es.js"></script>
  <script defer data-host="https://cusdis.com" data-app-id="2ab81401-18ec-4001-8032-c8e33288d5d6" src="https://cusdis.com/js/cusdis-count.umd.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <p>此页面不很优雅。如未回复请尝试邮件。
    <div id="cusdis_thread"
      data-host="https://cusdis.com"
      data-app-id="2ab81401-18ec-4001-8032-c8e33288d5d6"
      data-page-id="comments"
      data-page-url="https://numb.tech/comments"
      data-page-title="Guestbook">
    </div>

    <div class="comments-count">
      <span data-cusdis-count-page-id="comments">0</span> 条留言
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>